{
  "stem": "19211.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remember? 1944, '45, there was still a war going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time we were-- when the war ended, I-- we went to Krzemieniec, that town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in Poland, too, yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the war ended, after that then we traveled west.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like we went to Warsaw, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia is like south.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went by train mostly, mostly by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know the details really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents arranged things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know all the details about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me and my brother, and my mom, my dad, we all get together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember how, why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember from Vienna, then the Bricha came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- from Israel, they were helping us getting to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we were not allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's-- that's all I can tell you about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing eventful happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Poland to Czechoslovakia, from Czechoslovakia we went to Austria, Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Vienna we went to Munich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, we went to Nuremberg, Furth to Nuremberg, where Kissinger is from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Remember, he is from Furth, that city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went there because there was a DP camp, displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Furth.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went to that displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I tell you, my mom and my brother lived there from right after the war until '49, '49, maybe three or four years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a few years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Me?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed there for about a year or two, and then I went to school in Munich.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my dad worked in Munich for AJDC.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in uniform, and he was working for the food distribution.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was the manager, like, of the food distribution for the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was all sponsored by the Americans, you know, AJDC.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
